This repository's contents under `worker/` (Cloudflare Worker source,
wrangler config, package.json, and worker README) are vendored verbatim
from cardputer-claude-os. All credit for that code goes to its
upstream authors; only deployment configuration values (KV namespace
id, secrets) are intended to be changed locally.

The contents of `device/` are an original port of the Push-to-Claude
device application from MicroPython on the M5Stack Cardputer to
C++/Arduino on the M5Stack Core2, using the M5Unified library. The
port preserves the on-device protocol (raw WAV body to /ask, JSON
prompt to /ask-text, x-device-secret auth header) so the upstream
Worker continues to work unmodified.
